<b><h3>Baking is for everyone</b></h3>

<p>Baking is a hobby for all, no matter their ages. To bake, one requires only a few a things.
A few bowls, spoons, measuring equipments, an oven/oven microwave and the ingredients on your recipe. 
When you have all those things you can start baking! But how do we bake? We have everything laid out 
but we don't know what to do. It's simple, go to our website and click the recipes button. And voila! 
You have the instructions and ingredients all written down in one place. If you have any questions our
FAQs page is always ready. Plus our pro tips will help you to enhance your baking skills. Recorded sessions
are always availble for extra guidance and refrence. Happy baking bakers :)</p>


